news/frozen-fever-short-to-debut-in-front-of-disney-cinderella-1201369889;k=pmc-adi-31bb2464aad8b905af7a81e1d57b77ae|dead-url=no}}</ref>和《[[雪寶的佳節冒險|雪寶的佳節冒險]]》<ref name="Jun2017CS">{{cite news|last1=Perry|first1=Spencer|title=Olaf's Frozen Adventure Trailer Returns to the World of Frozen|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/trailers/858103-olafs-frozen-adventure-trailer-returns-to-the-world-of-frozen|accessdate=2017-06-13|work=ComingSoon.net|date=2017-06-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170617152723/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/trailers/858103-olafs-frozen-adventure-trailer-returns-to-the-world-of-frozen|archivedate=2017-06-17|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="Jun2017EW">{{cite news|last1=Snetiker|first1=Marc|title=Q&A: John Lasseter Debuts New 'Frozen' First Look|url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/06/13/olafs-frozen-adventure-john-lasseter-exclusive/|accessdate=2017-06-13|work=EW.com|date=2017-06-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614210149/http://ew.com/movies/2017/06/13/olafs-frozen-adventure-john-lasseter-exclusive/|archivedate=2017-06-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>中為阿克配音。

2014年起，葛洛夫開始在[[HBO|HBO]]的同性戀題材電視劇《[[三藩小時代|三藩小時代]]》中主演了電子遊戲設計師派翠克·莫瑞一角<ref>{{cite web|last=Schou|first=Solvej|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/glee-jonathan-groff-star-hbo-comedy-gay-friends-419996/|title='Glee's' Jonathan Groff to Star in HBO Comedy Pilot (Exclusive)|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2013-02-08|accessdate=2013-02-08|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707094617/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/glee-jonathan-groff-star-hbo-comedy-gay-friends-419996|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/jonathan-groff-hbo-gay-themed-comedy-522261/|title=HBO Greenlights Gay-Themed Dramedy Series|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2013-05-14|accessdate=2017-08-04|archive-date=2017-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716134409/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/jonathan-groff-hbo-gay-themed-comedy-522261|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但於2015年3月23日，HBO取消了《三藩小時代》，並改以電視電影的方式來完結<ref>{{cite web|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|title=''Looking'' Cancelled at HBO – But Patrick's Story Isn't Over Yet|url=http://tvline.com/2015/03/25/looking-cancelled-season-3-hbo-tv-movie/|website={{le|TVLine|TVLine}}|date=2015-03-25|accessdate=2017-08-04|archive-date=2017-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627212212/http://tvline.com/2015/03/25/looking-cancelled-season-3-hbo-tv-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年4月，他加入了同由HBO製作的電視電影《[[平常心|平常心]]》，他在片中飾演了克雷格·唐納一角<ref>{{cite web|last=Hibberd|first=James|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/04/26/jonathan-groff-ryan-murphy/|title=Jonathan Groff to play Taylor Kitsch's lover in Ryan Murphy film|website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-04-26|access-date=2013-04-26|archive-date=2014-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113075352/http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/04/26/jonathan-groff-ryan-murphy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他於2015年5月19日回到倫敦的舞台劇，並在[[皇家節日大廳|皇家節日大廳]]上的《{{le|一步登天 (音樂劇)|How to Succeed in Business Without Really Trying|一步登天}}》中演出，該場音樂劇就只辦這一次<ref>{{cite web|last=Shenton|first=Mark|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/jonathan-groff-to-star-in-london-concert-of-how-to-succeed-344085|title=Jonathan Groff To Star in London Concert of ''How to Succeed''|website=Playbill.com|date=2015-03-13|access-date=2015-05-25|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065132/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/jonathan-groff-to-star-in-london-concert-of-how-to-succeed-344085|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

