葛洛夫在20多歲時就被診斷出患有[[黑色素瘤|皮膚癌]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Dulin|first=Dann|url=http://www.aumag.org/2015/11/12/jonathan-groff/|title=Evolved Encounter: Jonathan Groff Mixes Reel Life with Real Life & Looks to the Beginning of the Epidemic for Wisdom|website=A&U Magazine|date=2015-11-12|access-date=2015-11-12|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610174813/http://www.aumag.org/2015/11/12/jonathan-groff/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年10月，葛洛夫在[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]舉行的{{le|全國平權遊行|National Equality March}}上公開宣布，自己是名[[同性戀|同性戀]]<ref name="Coming_out">{{cite web |last=Jensen |first=Michael |url=http://www.afterelton.com/people/2009/10/jonathan-groff-out |title=Tony Award Nominee Jonathan Groff has Most Low-key Coming Out Ever. |website=AfterElton.com |date=2009-10-19 |access-date=2012-02-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531032652/http://www.afterelton.com/people/2009/10/jonathan-groff-out |archivedate=2012-05-31 }}</ref>。2013年7月，葛洛夫與交往一年多的[[柴克瑞·恩杜|柴克瑞·恩杜]]和平分手，但兩人仍是朋友<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20130719/18339492|title=沙查甩拖結束同性戀情|website=[[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]]（香港）|date=2013-07-19|access-date=2017-08-03|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803132745/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20130719/18339492|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

作為[[LGBT|LGBT]]的倡導者，葛洛夫被《[[Out_(雜誌)|Out]]》旗下的《OUT100》列為2013年100個最引人注目的LGBT人之一；後於2014年，他與同胞{{le|莫瑞·巴特利特|Murray Bartlett}}和[[羅素·托維|羅素·托維]]一起主演了電視劇《[[三藩小時代|三藩小時代]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2013/2013/11/11/out100-jonathan-groff|title=Out100: Jonathan Groff|website=Out.com|date=2013-11-11|access-date=2015-05-08|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211521/http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2013/2013/11/11/out100-jonathan-groff|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Krochmal|first=Shana Naomi|url=http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2014/2014/11/04/out100-jonathan-groff-murray-bartlett-russell-tovey-looking|title=OUT100: Jonathan Groff & Murray Bartlett & Russell Tovey of Looking|website=Out.com|date=2015-11-04|access-date=2015-05-08|archive-date=2016-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901004521/http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2014/2014/11/04/out100-jonathan-groff-murray-bartlett-russell-tovey-looking|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，於2014年，他被[[拉維恩·考克斯|拉維恩·考克斯]]和{{le|國家LGBTQ專案組|National LGBTQ Task Force}}的執行長{{le|雷亞·凱利|Rea Carey}}評為[[紐約市LGBT驕傲遊行|紐約市LGBT驕傲遊行]]的大總帥<ref>{{cite web|last=Nichols|first=JamesMichael|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/22/2014-nyc-pride-grand-marshals_n_5191386.html|title=Laverne Cox, Jonathan Groff And Rea Carey Named 2014 NYC Pride Grand Marshals|website=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|date=2014-04-22|access-date=2015-05-08|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034921/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/04/22/2014-nyc-pride-grand-marshals_n_5191386.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年4月，葛洛夫被{{le|要點基金會 (LGBT)|Point Foundation (LGBT)|要點基金會}}授予Point Horizon獎<ref>{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Ashley|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/looking-star-jonathan-groff-be-780631|title=''Looking'' Star Jonathan Groff to Be Honored by Point Foundation (Exclusive)|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-03-11|access-date=2015-05-08|archive-date=2016-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120080830/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/looking-star-jonathan-groff-be-780631|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年12月，他被{{le|平等賓夕法尼亞州|Equality Pennsylvania}}頒發{{le|貝亞德·魯庭斯|Bayard Rustin}}獎，這象徵著身為賓夕法尼亞州人的他在LGBT領域上的努力獲得了肯定<ref>{{cite web|url=http://equalitypa.org/pasociety/|title=Equality PA Presents The Bayard Rustin Award & The Pioneering Advocacy Award to leaders in the LGBT Community|website=Equality Pennsylvania|access-date=2015-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120080830/http://equalitypa.org/pasociety/|archive-date=2016-01-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

